{"tid":1142104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東雕像藏1.3萬毒粉嶺華明邨兩男女被捕","createTime":"2019-05-07T01:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T06:11:55.000Z","uid":47352,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9c5363f641dd8c60485976b9d4f12260b2fa13","tid":1142104,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"警方根據線報，昨日晚上八時在粉嶺華明邨截查一名33歲男子，在他身上搜出一包約重14克冰毒，之後再在單位一個毛澤東雕像內檢獲一包約重10克的冰毒，黑市值約1.3萬，男子連同單位內的一名48歲女子，分別涉嫌藏毒及販毒被捕。警方相信已成功搗破一個供應毒品給上水一帶的毒品儲存中心。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20190507_20190507-051327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20190507_20190507-051327.jpg&h=305ef0cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e01a81e60e3614d894d6bec9f728dfa3714b5c5d","tid":1142104,"uid":28151,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:08:07.000Z","msg":"唔夾喺習語錄入面抵死"},{"pid":"ce2e452383c03b99bc75363dcd2d794f45a99d2a","tid":1142104,"uid":243635,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:27:01.000Z","msg":"骨灰龕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3eddb053462b9f57b7c18bda0b0a947f2136458","tid":1142104,"uid":113922,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:28:14.000Z","msg":"用維尼咪冇事"},{"pid":"f8d71383ee8885f5ba2a18cb00158d89d9f80447","tid":1142104,"uid":25688,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"呢招係大陸就話work啫，係香港用777像啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c16c532086b903fd54b11a64ad2f23ccd18e3e","tid":1142104,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:42:42.000Z","msg":"包*禍心"},{"pid":"41ef550bf86c0d8bb24de0204798ab2c0e33a57b","tid":1142104,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8d71383ee8885f5b